works.description: There is a stiff competition going on between the space tourism companies to offer the affluent adventurous journeys beyond the blue sky. Sir Richard Branson’s Virgin Galactic has now covered a crucial milestone, making space tourism closer to reality than ever before. For the very first time, the commercial spaceship has demonstrated its innovative reentry “feather” configuration. This unique feature lets the spaceship returns safely into the dense atmosphere from the vacuum of space.
